# todo Manager API

This is a simple todo Manager API built with Node.js, Express, and MongoDB. It allows users to create, read, update, and delete todos. User authentication is handled using JSON Web Tokens (JWT).

## Features

- User registration and login
- User authentication using JWT
- Create, read, update, and delete tasks
- Each task is associated with a user

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:

```sh
git clone https://github.com/sameena-parveen/simple-todo-app.git
cd task-manager-api
